author: Isabel Jones
title: Amber Tamblyn and David Cross Just Welcomed Their First Child
text:
A post shared by Amber Tamblyn (@amberrosetamblyn) on Feb 21, 2017 at 11:45am PST 
Knowing Tamblyn and her comedian husband’s kooky sense of humor, we’re assuming this exhaustive name is a joke—but you never know … We do like the idea of naming a child after feminist heroes Beyoncé and Ruth Bader Ginsburg , not sure about the Mustard Witch part though. 
WATCH: 2017's Most Adorable Celebrity Babies 
Anyway, we’re so excited for David and Amber and their newborn bundle of joy, baby Dauphinoise Petunia Brittany Scheherazade Von Funkinstein Mustard Witch RBG Cross Tamblyn-Bey jr.
